statements: SELECT * FROM trade_data;
SELECT trade_id, symbol, quantity FROM trade_data WHERE price > 100;
SELECT strategy_name, symbol, price FROM trade_data WHERE quantity >= 1000;
SELECT timestamp, strategy_name, symbol FROM trade_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, quantity, price FROM trade_data WHERE strategy_name = 'Scalping' ORDER BY quantity ASC;
SELECT * FROM trade_data WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT symbol, price FROM trade_data WHERE price < 50 ORDER BY trade_id ASC;
SELECT strategy_name, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM trade_data GROUP BY strategy_name ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;
SELECT COUNT(trade_id) AS trade_count, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM trade_data WHERE symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT strategy_name, MAX(quantity) AS max_quantity FROM trade_data GROUP BY strategy_name HAVING max_quantity > 500;
